subproject.corporate outcome: Capacities of national and local institutions enhanced to scale up proven MDG acceleration interventions and to plan, monitor, report and evaluate the MDG progress in the context of related national development priorities
subproject.description: This project aims to strengthen the National Assembly of Suriname in carrying out its core functions and responsibilities, based upon a comprehensive approach to parliamentary development. This project is in preparation of the full project document and will run for one year
subproject.title: Supporting the Sur Parliament
